---
title: Honey-Thyme Haloumi & Garlicky Pumpkin Toss with Almonds & Dill-Parsley Mayo
description: Sweet and fragrant also known as honey and thyme come together in a glaze for squeaky haloumi. Adding that hint of thyme really is the magic touch to elevating golden haloumi to the next level so it matches perfectly with a pumpkin and veggie toss.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/honey-thyme-haloumi-garlicky-pumpkin-toss-a229856d.jpg
